node.title: Multiple fatalities after crash south of Levin - police
node.description: Police say there are multiple fatalities after a crash between a truck and a car on State Highway 1, near Kuku in Horowhenua.
node.content: ["Police say there are multiple fatalities after a crash between a truck and a car on State Highway 1, near Kuku in Horowhenua.", "The crash was reported to police just after 3pm.", "Motorists are being asked to avoid the area.", "Police have not yet been able to confirm the number of dead and injured.", "The northbound lane of the highway,near the intersection of Kuku East Road, remains closed but is expected to be open this evening."]
